    <item>
      <title>K-99, a good candidate for dogs</title>
      <link>/en/blog/pauta_pet/</link>
      <pubDate>Sun, 06 Oct 2024 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>/en/blog/pauta_pet/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Article published in the &amp;ldquo;Espaço Aberto&amp;rdquo; section of the &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.estadao.com.br/opiniao/espaco-aberto/k-99-um-candidato-bom-para-os-cachorros/&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;online edition of &lt;em&gt;O Estado de S. Paulo&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, on Oct 6, 2024 (in Portuguese).&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I show the increase of themes related to the &amp;ldquo;pet agenda&amp;rdquo; in government programs for municipal elections between 2012 and 2024. Based on the results, I discuss the electoral and governance implications of these agendas, calling for them to be properly debated.&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
